18:58.679 --> 18:59.847
"I'm a Mac."

19:01.765 --> 19:04.393
"I'm a Mac." "I am a PC."
Never mind.

19:04.893 --> 19:06.645
Why do you wanna know?
You putting in spyware?

19:20.993 --> 19:24.079
Sir, you can't go in there.
If you don't work in engineering,

19:24.204 --> 19:25.289
you don't go in the lab.

19:25.539 --> 19:28.500
But, E-- Edmond Ku is in Nashville
and he asked me to check on things.

19:28.625 --> 19:30.627
