An inspiring step forward.

26:21.955 --> 26:22.956
Don.

26:23.873 --> 26:25.125
Avie is out.

26:30.880 --> 26:33.466
Good. He didn't understand the vision.

26:36.011 --> 26:38.305
You've told me everything
I need to know, right?

26:38.972 --> 26:39.973
<i>Yeah.</i>

26:40.140 --> 26:41.725
<i>I just got back from Nashville.</i>

26:42.100 --> 26:43.101
Don,

26:43.602 --> 26:46.271
- this is an inspiring step forward.
- Do you have a cold?

26:47.188 --> 26:48.189
N...

26:48.815 --> 26:50.317
No, I'm fine. I...

26:51.359 --> 26:52.360
Everything's fine.

27:02.037 --> 27:04.039
So, how was Nashville?

27:05.040 --> 27:08.084
I can't talk about it.
It's... you know, NDA.

27:09.044 --> 27:11.671
What? Oh, this is terrible.

27:12.339 --> 27:15.884
Suddenly, everyone's on
a need-to-know basis, well I need to know.

27:16.092 --> 27:18.970
I mean, my whole job is needing to know.

27:24.434 --> 27:25.435
Uh...

27:27.896 --> 27:28.897
Who's that?

27:29.773 --> 27:33.610
That is Brendan Morris.
She brought in a new engineer.

27:34.027 --> 27:36.071
We're not moving fast enough apparently.

27:36.655 --> 27:37.906
We don't know what's he's working on.

27:38.031 --> 27:40.367
He just goes into the office
and shuts the door.

27:40.867 --> 27:41.868
Hmm.

27:42.619 --> 27:45.038
Hang on. I've got an idea.

27:54.714 --> 27:55.632
Yeah.

27:56.049 --> 27:57.967
Good day, sir. I have the package
you ordered,

27:58.134 --> 28:00.804
and I think it's best that I come in
to your office and set it down.

28:01.721 --> 28:03.390
That box is already open,

28:03.556 --> 28:05.433
and it's got an empty Snapple bottle
inside of it.

28:08.978 --> 28:10.105
Well, you ordered it.

28:10.689 --> 28:13.400
So, yeah, if you're
the one who ordered it, then I...

28:14.484 --> 28:18.071
- Damn.
