This is an inspiring step forward.

34:39.619 --> 34:40.620
Forward.

34:41.496 --> 34:42.497
Forward.

34:42.580 --> 34:43.581
Forward.

34:43.664 --> 34:48.419
This is an inspiring step forward.

35:05.728 --> 35:07.313
I shouldn't have had you meet me here.

35:07.480 --> 35:09.524
I just thought this would be better
face to face.

35:11.150 --> 35:12.401
Drive around the block.

35:43.891 --> 35:45.893
All right. Very nice.

35:47.061 --> 35:49.647
It's, uh-- it's not there yet
but we're getting closer.

35:49.981 --> 35:52.233
- I think it needs a name.
- How about Glue Bot?

35:53.860 --> 35:55.069
Edison.

35:56.612 --> 35:58.447
I'm calling it the Edison.

36:00.074 --> 36:02.076
And this is the direction
that we're going in.

36:27.059 --> 36:29.520
- No, sir. I can't let you take that thing.
- No. Wait. No, that's my Exacto knife.

36:29.645 --> 36:31.272
It is not the intellectual property
of Theranos.

36:31.355 --> 36:33.065
- Just doing my job, sir.
- Come on. It's his Exacto knife.

36:33.191 --> 36:34.275
Sir, please take a step back.

36:34.358 --> 36:36.235
It is my Exacto knife
and I like the way it cuts things.

36:36.319 --> 36:38.404
Please, sir. I'm gonna need you
to take a step back, all right?

36:38.487 --> 36:39.989
Okay. Just take it, but...

36:49.165 --> 36:51.167
Uh, I...

36:52.835 --> 36:55.796
I don't have my car today.
So, if, um...

36:56.172 --> 36:58.424
uh, someone can, uh, give me

36:58.549 --> 37:00.092
the number of a cab company...

37:03.471 --> 37:04.639
All right, let's go.

38:02.113 --> 38:03.114
Elizabeth?

38:06.784 --> 38:08.244
I'm sorry,
I thought she was here.

38:14.208 --> 38:15.251
I here.

38:16.335 --> 38:17.336
I'm here.

38:18.504 --> 38:20.506
- Oh, hey.
- What's going on?

38:20.715 --> 38:22.174
The legal team is ready to see you.

38:24.010 --> 38:26.262
Elizabeth, I need to talk to you.

38:28.431 --> 38:30.891
I'm so sorry.
I was on a very long phone call.

38:32.143 --> 38:35.062
Hi. What... What's going on
with the filing of the lawsuit?

38:35.146 --> 38:37.356
Did you do trials
on terminal cancer patients

38:37.481 --> 38:39.400
with a prototype that didn't work?

38:40.693 --> 38:42.611
Uh, can we have the room, please?

38:43.654 --> 38:44.655
Answer me.

38:44.905 --> 38:47.575
- Where did you hear that? Avie?
- Is it a secret?

38:47.825 --> 38:50.202
No. Uh... no, I just, uh...

38:50.411 --> 38:52.997
That goes against everything
I believe in.

38:53.122 --> 38:54.999
- Ana, it was a trial.
- And I have moral obligation

38:55.124 --> 38:57.376
- to talk to you about the ethics...
- Everybody does trials.

38:59.712 --> 39:04.425
You know, I was trying to remember
what it was I saw in you, why I came here,

39:05.343 --> 39:09.180
and... I don't know, I think
I thought you were like me somehow.

39:09.889 --> 39:10.890
An outsider.

39:11.515 --> 39:14.769
I am. That's why I have to fight
to keep my job.

39:14.935 --> 39:17.521
No. That's why you have to care more.

39:17.813 --> 39:20.566
I only came here because I thought
we were helping people.

39:20.691 --> 39:22.777
I can't help anybody
if I don't have a company.

39:22.985 --> 39:25.029
- That's not the point.
- Yes, it is.

39:25.363 --> 39:28.240
I don't know
what you want from me.

39:28.366 --> 39:32.828
I... You told me to be more of a CEO,
and so I'm trying to do that.

39:33.079 --> 39:34.830
I'm trying. I'm trying.

39:34.997 --> 39:37.041
So sorry, but Elizabeth,
I really need you.

39:39.418 --> 39:43.089
We can discuss this later.
Okay? Ana, please.

39:48.302 --> 39:50.221
No. I'm quitting.

39:51.889 --> 39:53.516
My whole team is quitting.

40:06.153 --> 40:08.656
Make sure Ana doesn't leave
the building with any property.

40:08.823 --> 40:10.658
- I will.
- Oh, and she needs to sign an NDA.

40:10.866 --> 40:12.910
- The design team quit.
- Yeah.

40:13.536 --> 40:15.996
And one of them told me to give you
these books on management.

40:19.667 --> 40:20.918
I think it's a joke.

40:23.504 --> 40:26.757
Why is Don Lucas in my office?

40:27.800 --> 40:31.178
I don't know. That's why I came
and got you. He just showed up.

40:39.687 --> 40:41.105
Hey, Don. I didn't know
that you were coming in.

40:41.230 --> 40:42.231
Shut the door.

40:47.403 --> 40:50.156
How... how are you doing?

40:55.661 --> 40:58.497
Not one of these contracts
is even close to being done.

41:00.207 --> 41:01.208
I know.

41:02.084 --> 41:05.171
I just... I didn't want
to alert the board of...

41:05.379 --> 41:07.256
- to the mechanics...
- Stop the game!

41:08.257 --> 41:11.427
I just spent an hour with your accountant
going over all of this.

41:15.431 --> 41:16.640
You lied to me.

41:19.768 --> 41:21.020
You lied to me.

41:25.232 --> 41:29.862
I know things have not been going
as smoothly as they should have...

41:30.362 --> 41:31.363
and that's my fault.

41:32.198 --> 41:35.784
But I brought on Brendan Morris
who is developing the...

41:35.951 --> 41:38.746
- a version of our prototype.
- I'm going to call for a vote

41:38.871 --> 41:40.206
of no confidence from the board.

41:42.166 --> 41:44.877
You'll no longer be CEO of Theranos.

41:47.880 --> 41:49.507
You had a good idea.

41:50.508 --> 41:52.801
You're just not ready yet.

42:33.092 --> 42:34.093
Tess...

42:35.844 --> 42:37.388
Could you, um...

42:38.264 --> 42:39.265
make me an appointment

42:39.723 --> 42:41.225
at the Genius Bar, please?

43:03.455 --> 43:04.999
What was the name for the account?

43:07.960 --> 43:09.545
Elizabeth Holmes.

43:21.473 --> 43:23.225
Good news. You're insured,
so we can just go ahead

43:23.309 --> 43:24.351
and replace the entire phone today.

43:26.645 --> 43:27.980
Do you wanna give me your phone?

43:28.314 --> 43:30.065
Are you gonna be able to see what's on it?

43:30.733 --> 43:32.359
Just for a few seconds.
I'm gonna go ahead

43:32.443 --> 43:34.194
and back it up to our drive.
Should only take a few minutes.

43:35.321 --> 43:37.031
Your secrets are safe with me.

43:43.621 --> 43:45.539
So, how are you?

43:45.748 --> 43:47.583
I know it can be hard
being without your phone.

43:48.459 --> 43:51.128
You from around here?
Do you go to, like, school nearby?

43:53.547 --> 43:54.798
Stanford.

43:55.215 --> 43:56.467
Oh, awesome!

43:57.217 --> 43:58.844
I'm kind of in-between schools
at the moment,

43:58.927 --> 44:01.680
so I thought I'd work as a genius
until I can figure out what I wanna do.

44:04.224 --> 44:05.434
What was your dream as a child?

44:08.646 --> 44:09.730
As a child?

44:11.023 --> 44:13.567
No, I don't think
I had any dreams as a child.

44:15.027 --> 44:16.195
That sounds nice.

44:17.196 --> 44:18.197
What does?

44:20.074 --> 44:23.369
