Why are you scared? You can do anything.
Anything that you want.

44:32.127 --> 44:33.087
Thank you.

44:33.253 --> 44:37.383
Because it... it doesn't really matter.
Right? Nothing you do will matter

44:37.508 --> 44:40.260
because you don't really care.

44:41.720 --> 44:43.097
I mean, you...

44:43.430 --> 44:47.184
you have no ambition.
You don't wanna do anything important.

44:48.227 --> 44:49.436
You're just a person.

44:54.024 --> 44:55.109
Uh...

44:55.734 --> 44:57.277
Now, it should, um...

45:01.281 --> 45:04.451
Oh, no. No, no.

45:07.621 --> 45:11.083
I don't know what happened,
but, um, all of your information is...

45:12.251 --> 45:14.461
I mean, it's just... it's gone.

45:15.421 --> 45:17.673
I'm so sorry, I...

45:19.383 --> 45:21.051
I did everything right.

45:21.135 --> 45:27.266
I mean, I followed all of the steps.
I was just too quick to... I'm so sorry.

45:47.786 --> 45:48.996
Elizabeth, we're ready for you.

46:04.219 --> 46:05.220
Ah, Elizabeth.

46:08.098 --> 46:11.018
You are here
because we, collectively,

46:12.144 --> 46:14.438
have lost confidence in your ability

46:15.606 --> 46:17.900
to continue on as CEO of this company.

46:18.358 --> 46:20.694
You have misrepresented
the revenue stream.

46:20.778 --> 46:24.156
You have been unable
to manage research and development.

46:24.615 --> 46:27.534
