47:08.242 --> 47:10.953
should step in as acting CEO

47:11.036 --> 47:12.955
until we can find somebody else.

47:14.373 --> 47:15.999
Of course, yeah. I...

47:17.209 --> 47:18.293
I understand.

47:24.800 --> 47:25.926
I just...

47:27.928 --> 47:29.096
I did everything right.

47:30.389 --> 47:33.392
I... I followed all the steps.

47:39.064 --> 47:40.190
I did it too quick.

47:42.109 --> 47:43.277
And I'm sorry.

47:44.444 --> 47:45.612
I got ahead of myself,

47:46.363 --> 47:51.493
and all your concerns are valid.
You're right. I am in over my head.

47:54.204 --> 47:55.414
I'm just a girl

47:56.582 --> 47:59.418
who had a dream
to change the world,

48:00.210 --> 48:04.339
and I just didn't realize
how hard it was gonna be.

48:05.299 --> 48:10.512
I need help. You're absolutely right.
I need adult supervision.

48:17.227 --> 48:18.270
And that's...

48:19.479 --> 48:22.524
that's why I reached out
to an old friend

48:24.026 --> 48:27.946
to come on board and help me.

48:30.282 --> 48:33.619
He offered to bring in 20 million dollars

48:34.703 --> 48:36.580
and come on as COO,

48:37.205 --> 48:41.126
but only if I'm still the CEO, obviously.

48:42.461 --> 48:43.670
But that's up to you.

48:44.922 --> 48:45.923
Don,

48:47.174 --> 48:48.175
can you forgive me?

48:52.179 --> 48:53.180
Um...

48:54.723 --> 48:57.893
He had an idea that I'd love
to get your advice on.

48:59.561 --> 49:04.024
He thinks that we should
forget pharmaceutical companies

49:04.232 --> 49:07.694
and try to target retail.
Create our own retail space,

49:07.819 --> 49:09.363
like an Apple store.

49:12.407 --> 49:15.077
I don't know. What do you think?

49:23.877 --> 49:25.587
- I'm in here.

49:50.612 --> 49:52.114
It's not working between us.

49:54.282 --> 49:55.492
I know that.

49:59.413 --> 50:02.165
You can stay here for a while
until you find your own place.

50:03.375 --> 50:04.668
- I'll move out.
- No.

50:05.419 --> 50:06.420
No.

50:07.504 --> 50:09.256
Oh, come on, I can't let you move out.

50:09.339 --> 50:10.340
No.

50:10.757 --> 50:12.009
Come work with me.

50:21.560 --> 50:22.686
Do you want that?

50:28.525 --> 50:30.777
I need a 20-million-dollar investment.

50:36.241 --> 50:38.493
So the board will keep you as CEO.

50:45.375 --> 50:47.127
You already told them you had it.

50:48.879 --> 50:49.880
Yes.

50:54.843 --> 50:55.844
Twelve million.

50:57.471 --> 51:00.098
Twenty. And you can be COO.

51:33.715 --> 51:34.758
I quit.

51:35.967 --> 51:38.553
Come on. Come on. Come on.

52:07.249 --> 52:08.917
She's suing me?

52:09.417 --> 52:12.546
Are you kidding?
Nah, I'm not taking those.

52:12.796 --> 52:17.425
I am not taking those. Hey! Hey!

52:24.015 --> 52:27.978
And by the end of 2008,
Sunny Balwani came along as COO,

52:28.728 --> 52:30.856
and you bought back some shares
of the company.

52:32.107 --> 52:33.859
Yes, I had a controlling stake.

52:39.990 --> 52:40.991
Ready?

54:19.631 --> 54:20.924
<i>I want to be a billionaire.</i>

54:22.842 --> 54:25.428
ELIZABETH:<i> It's not about the money.</i>
<i>You have to have a purpose.</i>

54:25.845 --> 54:28.306
- What are you afraid of?
-<i>I can't do one thing wrong.</i>

54:28.682 --> 54:30.684
<i>I can't give them one reason</i>
<i>to doubt me.</i>

54:32.227 --> 54:34.562
<i>I'm gonna be on the cutting edge</i>
<i>of healthcare.</i>

54:34.854 --> 54:36.773
<i>It's going to change the world.</i>

54:37.357 --> 54:38.566
JAY ROSAN:<i> Everything's changing.</i>

54:38.650 --> 54:42.070
These kids don't get bogged down about
the way things have always been done,

54:43.446 --> 54:45.115
<i>They want to change things now!</i>

54:45.615 --> 54:48.201
<i>We launch in 48 hours!</i>
We did it!

54:48.618 --> 54:50.245
PHYLLIS GARDNER:
<i>I don't believe a word she says.</i>

54:51.496 --> 54:52.956
<i>There's something going on!</i>

54:53.081 --> 54:55.208
Why are they not actively seeking
FDA approval.

54:55.292 --> 54:56.835
Her whole image, is fake!

54:57.627 --> 55:00.630
- You don't understand the business.
- And you don't understand the science!

55:01.006 --> 55:03.341
ELIZABETH:<i> This isn't just my company,</i>
<i>this is who I am.</i>

55:03.800 --> 55:06.386
There's only one thing you need to know
about Elizabeth, she's a fraud.

55:06.678 --> 55:09.347
I know you want to believe
everything she's saying is real.

55:09.597 --> 55:12.100
The way Theranos is operating,
someone is gonna get killed.

55:12.684 --> 55:13.935
You're going to lose everything.

55:16.146 --> 55:18.356
No, I'm fine. Everything's fine.
